data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This remarkable ranch-style house features an inviting open floor plan that is sure to meet all your needs. Step inside and be delighted by the thoughtfully designed split bedroom floorplan, ensuring the perfect blend of privacy and functionality. Enjoy your own side of the house while your family or guests have their own dedicated space. The primary suite of this home is truly impressive, boasting a massive size that provides ample room for relaxation. You'll also find a generously sized walk-in closet for all your storage needs, as well as a convenient en suite bathroom, creating a private oasis within your own home. Situated on the tranquil cul de sac of Cybelle Court, this house offers a serene location while remaining just minutes away from all the amenities you desire. Whether you're seeking vibrant nightlife, convenient shopping options, delectable dining experiences, or recreation in nearby parks, you'll find it all within reach. For the culinary enthusiast, the kitchen is a true delight. With plenty of counter space and top-of-the-line appliances, it's the perfect place to prepare and showcase hors d'oeuvres for your holiday parties. You can also enjoy baking cookies for a local food drive before cozying up by the fireplace in the inviting living room. Recent updates to this lovely Miamisburg home include a new refrigerator (2018) and a newer HVAC system (2019) ensuring modern convenience and efficiency. Don't miss out on the endless possibilities this home has to offer. Embrace the open floor plan, relish in the privacy of the split bedroom layout, and take advantage of the numerous updates.
